(44, 19, 34, 66, 13, 4, 4, 'Great is Diana of the Ephesians', 'Worship and Idolatry Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of worship in both passages. In Acts, the crowd worships Diana, while in Revelation, the worship is directed towards the beast and the dragon.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
